  skip = "current",
  text = [[

          - Fire Temple -

Link journeys to the heart of the
Death Mountain and explores
this Dungeon built within it.
Find the Dungeon item and
use it to reach
your goal.
Difficulty : 7/10
Objective : Obtain the Dungeon item
Tip : Fire lights torches.
]],
}

dialog{
  id = "LABORS.tott.paintings.hylia_waterfall",
  skip = "current",
  text = [[

       - Hylia Waterfalls -

This region is a passage
to reach the Icy Peak
and the Wind Ruins.
It is said that a Great Fairy exists
in this place... your goal
will be to find her and help her.
Difficulty : 5/10
Objective : Save the Great Fairy
Tip : Night attracts Gems.
]],
}

dialog{
  id = "LABORS.tott.paintings.ice_cave",
  skip = "current",
  text = [[

       - Snow Peak Puzzle -

Link will have to rack his brain to
solve these ice block puzzles... Help
him and prove that you have a brain.
Difficulty : 7/10
Objective : Solve the puzzles
Tip : Ice is slippery.
]],
}

