dialog{
  id = "LABORS.tott.paintings.water_temple",
  skip = "current",
  text = [[

          - Water Temple -

Link faces here his future biggest
trauma... and soon
yours, possibly.
Stay focused, take notes, and don't
lose your mind. Everything
should be fine.
Difficulty : 8/10
Objective : Complete the Dungeon
Tip : Good luck
]],
}

dialog{
  id = "LABORS.zeldo_wave_1.after_battle",
  text = [[
It seems you're not as
pathetic as I thought after all.

I'll let you access the next
floor of the Castle.

But get ready, because next time,
I won't be so merciful with you !
]],
}

dialog{
  id = "LABORS.zeldo_wave_1.battle_start",
  text = [[
Try not to disappoint me...$0
En garde !
]],
}

dialog{
  id = "LABORS.zeldo_wave_1.beaten",
