So you never give up, huh ?
]],
}

dialog{
  id = "LABORS.zeldo_wave_1.end_1st_floor",
  text = [[
You've managed to complete
this first Wave of
content ! Well done !
To celebrate, I've got myself
a brand new look !
Thanks, DarkDavy15 !
]],
}

dialog{
  id = "LABORS.zeldo_wave_1.end_1st_floor_alt",
  skip = "current",
  text = [[
You're back again. Couldn't help
dying, huh ? Because of you,
I have to change again.
Behold and admire
Zeldo the Magnificent, version 2.0.
]],
}

dialog{
  id = "LABORS.zeldo_wave_1.give_sword",
  text = [[
I'll give you a little help.
You clearly need it...
Take this legendary weapon !
]],
}

dialog{
  id = "LABORS.zeldo_wave_1.spell_sprite",
  skip = "current",
  text = [[
smoke:set_enabled('true')
zeldo:set_sprite('enemies/boss/
