dialog{
  id = "end.end_beta",
  text = [[
Congratulations and thank you again for
completing this beta version of
Forgotten Legend.
Feel free to leave me
your feedback on the game's content.

Your feedback will help me
create a better gaming experience for you.
Also, feel free to follow me on Twitch or YouTube.
You will be quickly informed
of the project's development
and the arrival of a future version.
My ultimate goal is to create
a purely classic Zelda
that would be close to what
Nintendo themselves could
have released... I aim for a vast
adventure comprising more than
9 Dungeons and about twenty
hours of gameplay.

Thank you for making this dream
possible !

If you wish to continue exploring
the world of Forgotten
Legend, let me help you :
I offer you an Ocarina and the
Song of Soaring. They will
allow you to travel quickly.
However, know that these items
are not supposed to be obtained 
at this stage of the game and will be
removed for future beta versions...

I believe everything has been said. Thank
you for your contribution and don't
forget to share your feedback.

 :)
]],
}

dialog{
  id = "end.get_heroic_mode",
