completing the game.

As a reward, here's a
little gift : the heroic mode !

In this mode, enemies will
deal twice as much
damage to you.
When you start a
new game in the future, you
can choose to play in
heroic mode or not.
Have fun and good luck if
you're up for the challenge !
]],
}

