to make your life easier
will appear :
Arrows, tiles, and more...
Zeldo has been very cunning,
he admits it. If you find
the game too difficult,
don't hesitate to
activate this Card !
Remember that this Card
is only valid in this Wave
and can be deactivated at
any time in the Quest Status !
]],
}

